ai-ja251:1.1_0: “The thought is stuck in what is not the thought,
ai-ja251:1.2_0: you’re stuck in your own thoughts.
ai-ja251:2.1_0: Not by ear nor by nose,
ai-ja251:3.1_0: I don’t see any such moderations,
ai-ja251:3.2_0: from which today I call a “live”
ai-ja251:3.3_0: as far as the mind doesn’t know it.
ai-ja251:3.4_0: My task has used to be eaten suffering.”
